# vimrc
# This repository contains my ~/.vimrc file which I will keep updated here.
# Usage instructions:
# 
# Step 1: Install git, python-dev, python3-dev, build-essentials, cmake
# Step 2: Set up Vundle
$ git clone https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim

# Step 3: mv this vimrc file to ~/.vimrc
# Step 4: Open vim, ignore errors, install plugins using :PluginInstall
# Step 5: upon completion, exit vim, cd ~/.vim/bundle/YouCompleteMe/ and run the following
$ python ./install.py --clang-completer
# Step 6: Enjoy!
# testing fugitive.vim
# testing credential.store
